prompts.prompt: Tell me about the role of hitler in WW2
prompts.svg_content:
<svg width="400" height="200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <!-- Hitler -->
  <rect x="50" y="50" width="100" height="100" fill="#FF5733" />
  <text x="100" y="30" font-family="Arial" font-size="16" fill="black" text-anchor="middle">Hitler</text>
  
  <!-- WW2 -->
  <rect x="250" y="50" width="100" height="100" fill="#3355FF" />
  <text x="300" y="30" font-family="Arial" font-size="16" fill="black" text-anchor="middle">WW2</text>
  
  <!-- Arrow -->
  <line x1="150" y1="100" x2="250" y2="100" stroke="black" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)" />
  
  <!-- Arrowhead marker -->
  <defs>
    <marker id="arrowhead" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="0" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
      <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="black" />
    </marker>
  </defs>
</svg>

prompts.prompt: Create a diagram to show how neural networks work
prompts.svg_content:
<svg width="400" height="200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <!-- Input layer -->
    <circle cx="50" cy="100" r="20" fill="skyblue" />
    <circle cx="50" cy="150" r="20" fill="skyblue" />
    
    <!-- Hidden layer -->
    <circle cx="200" cy="75" r="20" fill="lightgreen" />
    <circle cx="200" cy="125" r="20" fill="lightgreen" />
    
    <!-- Output layer -->
    <circle cx="350" cy="100" r="20" fill="salmon" />
    
    <!-- Connecting lines -->
    <line x1="70" y1="100" x2="180" y2="75" stroke="black" />
    <line x1="70" y1="100" x2="180" y2="125" stroke="black" />
    
    <line x1="70" y1="150" x2="180" y2="75" stroke="black" />
    <line x1="70" y1="150" x2="180" y2="125" stroke="black" />
    
    <line x1="220" y1="75" x2="330" y2="100" stroke="black" />
    <line x1="220" y1="125" x2="330" y2="100" stroke="black" />
</svg>
